          // prints &quot;The creator is Aaron&quot;
        }).then( () =&gt; {


Arrays of refs work the same way. Just call the populate
method on the query and an array of documents will be returned in place of the original _ids.
It is important to match the type of _id to the type of ref (see this example):
const personSchema = Schema({
  _id     : Number,
