Story
.find(...)
.populate(&#39;fans&#39;)
.populate(&#39;_creator&#39;)
.exec()

Query conditions and other options
What if we wanted to populate our fans array based on their age, select just their names, and return at most, any 5 of them?
Story
.find(...)
.populate({
  path: &#39;fans&#39;,
  match: { age: { $gte: 21 }},
  select: &#39;name -_id&#39;,
  options: { limit: 5 }
})
.exec()


